<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Kincora</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">One of the most sought-after residential neighborhoods in the Symons Valley development, Kincora lies in the northwest quadrant of Calgary and is represented by Ward 2 Councilor in the Calgary City Council. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood is located at the northern edge of the city and is bound by the <a href="/sage-hill.php">Sage Hill</a> community on the north, the <a href="/sherwood.php">Sherwood</a> community on the west, the <a href="/evanston.php">Evanston</a> community on the east and the <a href="/hidden-valley.php">Hidden Valley</a> on the south.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Kincora comprise some of the most affordable residential units in the city ranging from single-family detached homes to apartment condos and townhomes, which are typically available at an average price of $500,000. </p>
        </div>
